115void CacheStorageEngineConnection::reference(uint64_t cacheIdentifier)
116{
117 CACHE_STORAGE_RELEASE_LOG("reference cache %" PRIu64, cacheIdentifier);
118 ASSERT(m_cachesLocks.isValidKey(cacheIdentifier));
119 if (!m_cachesLocks.isValidKey(cacheIdentifier))
120 return;
121
122 auto& counter = m_cachesLocks.ensure(cacheIdentifier, []() {
123 return 0;
124 }).iterator->value;
125 if (!counter++)
126 Engine::lock(m_connection.networkProcess(), sessionID(), cacheIdentifier);
127}

129void CacheStorageEngineConnection::dereference(uint64_t cacheIdentifier)
130{
131 CACHE_STORAGE_RELEASE_LOG("dereference cache %" PRIu64, cacheIdentifier);
132 ASSERT(m_cachesLocks.isValidKey(cacheIdentifier));
133 if (!m_cachesLocks.isValidKey(cacheIdentifier))
134 return;
135
136 auto referenceResult = m_cachesLocks.find(cacheIdentifier);
137 if (referenceResult == m_cachesLocks.end())
138 return;
139
140 ASSERT(referenceResult->value);
141 if (--referenceResult->value)
142 return;
143
144 Engine::unlock(m_connection.networkProcess(), sessionID(), cacheIdentifier);
145 m_cachesLocks.remove(referenceResult);
146}
